      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior shows some minor signs of use, including a few light rock chips and small surface scratches, but it still presents very well overall. Inside, the cabin is clean and all features are fully functional. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner.",
