    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it offers a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality. From the precision-engineered performance to the pristine aesthetic details, this car is a testament to superior ownership and uncompromising care. For the collector who demands perfection, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
